{"tid":1234103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失敗主義不是無為的理由","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:06:36.000Z","uid":143210,"like":185,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3f18ad874cd330251a8046b64abfd7a7885b6947","tid":1234103,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:51.000Z","msg":"好多post講話會重蹈雨傘嘅覆轍<br />\n<br />\n分化，佔路失民心<br />\n<br />\n但大家明明都已經有呢啲資訊，點解唔可以宣傳畀人呢<br />\n<br />\n對住思維錯誤嘅人，我地唔係廢事同佢講，而係要大大聲，因為道理係我地度！學唐僧咁！<br />\n<br />\n屌人哋屌你時，都唔可以變成同佢地一樣敵視對方<br />\n<br />\n雖然難受，但要說服一個人<span style=\"color: orange;\">放下身段釋出善意好重要</span><br />\n<br />\n最後大家都一定要記得<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山</span>，重點係一齊爬，行動時機一致<br />\n<br />\n我地要走出分化困局！！"},{"pid":"d7c94e89fb2b62c830c28397e238b703a871c097","tid":1234103,"uid":60563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"set deadline 行動升級<br />\n就算今日再有200萬人出黎都係一樣<br />\n淋病照樣撚狗咁撚我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae28950acbd68df626cb3b8c42f7e6ed05af912a","tid":1234103,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fee78be622cb92bccf26e62eb8945c2d03d49739","tid":1234103,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb7d3eb3a8d45c609f6ae256d335277242da2f7b","tid":1234103,"uid":210612,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"熱門區已經係失敗主義"},{"pid":"8ae6bd712612631f2be1d0d19534f5337fafca7d","tid":1234103,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05eab76c87a4687dad5c579d80c133d414aae021","tid":1234103,"uid":143210,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fb7d3eb3a8d45c609f6ae256d335277242da2f7b","tid":1234103,"uid":210612,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"熱門區已經係